        <updateDate>2012-06-19T17:18:11Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>21st Century Language Act of 2012 - Removes references to the word &quot;lunatic&quot; from rules of construction of the U.S. Code and banking law provisions concerning: (1) trust powers of banks, and (2) bank consolidations and mergers.</p>]]></text>
